00:00:42,042 --> 00:00:43,835
IT'S HARD TO
BELIEVE...

14
00:00:43,835 --> 00:00:45,545
I NEVER THOUGHT WE'D
JOIN FORCES

15
00:00:45,545 --> 00:00:47,547
WITH THE
UNION AND THE AEU.

16
00:00:50,884 --> 00:00:53,136
Sergei:
LIKE IT'S ONE BIG PARTY.

17
00:00:55,138 --> 00:00:57,683
Kati:
LIEUTENANT, HOW'S YOUR
DUST‐PROOFING HOLDING UP?

18
00:00:57,683 --> 00:00:59,685
