COLONEL!

19
00:00:59,685 --> 00:01:00,936
WATCH ME GO TO WORK!

20
00:01:00,936 --> 00:01:03,438
CAPTURING A GUNDAM WILL
BE A SNAP WITH THIS!

21
00:01:03,438 --> 00:01:04,231
IMPOSSIBLE.

22
00:01:04,231 --> 00:01:05,190
OH, COME ON!

23
00:01:07,734 --> 00:01:10,737
OVER FLAGS ARE TO REMAIN
ON STANDBY UNTIL ORDERED.

24
00:01:10,737 --> 00:01:12,447
Graham:
ROGER THAT.

25
00:01:12,447 --> 00:01:14,324
52 TEAMS IN TOTAL...

26
00:01:14,324 --> 00:01:17,411
832 MOBILE SUITS
PARTICIPATING.

27
00:01:18,328 --> 00:01:21,123
YOU MAY CALL US COWARDS
FOR THIS...

28
00:01:21,123 --> 00:01:25,085
BUT I'LL FOLLOW THE MILITARY'S
PLAN ON THIS ONE...GUNDAMS.

