00:02:35,197 --> 00:02:54,800
♪

34
00:03:02,724 --> 00:03:03,725
HMM...

35
00:03:10,065 --> 00:03:12,984
LOUISE, HOW MUCH LONGER
ARE YOU GOING TO BE LIKE THIS?

36
00:03:12,984 --> 00:03:14,820
I'M DEPRESSED BECAUSE
MOM WENT HOME.

37
00:03:14,820 --> 00:03:16,321
I KNOW THAT.

38
00:03:17,406 --> 00:03:18,865
PLEASE CHEER ME UP.

39
00:03:18,865 --> 00:03:20,992
CHEER UP, LOUISE‐‐

40
00:03:20,992 --> 00:03:23,370
I MEAN, BUY ME THINGS!
PLEASE.

41
00:03:23,370 --> 00:03:24,413
HUH?

42
00:03:34,047 --> 00:03:36,341
I CAN'T BUY THOSE, LOUISE!

43
00:03:36,341 --> 00:03:37,968
I CAN'T AFFORD BRAND‐NAME
ITEMS LIKE THAT!

44
00:03:37,968 --> 00:03:39,261
(Growling)

45
00:03:39,261 --> 00:03:41,471
SAJI, I WANT YOU
TO BUY THEM FOR ME!

46
00:03:41,471 --> 00:03:42,472
I CAN'T.

47
00:03:42,472 --> 00:03:43,723
BUY THEM,
BUY THEM, BUY THEM!

48
00:03:43,723 --> 00:03:45,851
WHAT ARE THOSE
KIDS UP TO?

49
00:03:45,851 --> 00:03:48,186
SO INNOCENT
AND PEACEFUL,

50
00:03:48,186 --> 00:03:50,272
AND WITH NEARLY
A THOUSAND MOBILE SUITS

51
00:03:50,272 --> 00:03:52,482
GETTING READY TO TAKE PART
IN A HUGE EXERCISE.

52
00:03:54,109 --> 00:03:56,027
I WISH EVERYONE
WAS THAT PEACEFUL.

53
00:03:57,362 --> 00:03:59,823
(Sighs)

54
00:03:59,823 --> 00:04:02,200
(Thinking):
I WONDER, WAS THIS
GIGANTIC EXERCISE

55
00:04:02,200 --> 00:04:05,287
IN YOUR PLANS, TOO...
AEOLIA SCHENBERG?

56
00:04:11,251 --> 00:04:13,462
Chairman:
HOW IS EVERYTHING
PROGRESSING?

57
00:04:13,462 --> 00:04:16,631
WE'VE JUST RECEIVED A
REPORT FROM INTELLIGENCE.

58
00:04:16,631 --> 00:04:19,050
THE LATEST UPDATE HAS THREE
MOBILE SUITS

59
00:04:19,050 --> 00:04:20,927
AND THREE PERSONNEL
TRANSPORTS HEADING FOR

60
00:04:20,927 --> 00:04:23,096
THE URANIUM STORAGE
FACILITY.

61
00:04:23,513 --> 00:04:26,558
NOW IF ONLY OUR TRUE QUARRY
WOULD GET CAUGHT IN THE NET.

62
00:04:29,561 --> 00:04:31,188
VERY WELL THEN.

63
00:04:31,188 --> 00:04:34,191
IT SEEMS THE TWO WAY
COMMUNICATION SYSTEM HAS

64
00:04:34,191 --> 00:04:37,611
DETECTED SOME "INTERFERENCE"
AT THE EXERCISE GROUND.

65
00:04:37,611 --> 00:04:41,490
AS WE EXPECTED. ADVISE THE
COMMANDER TO CHANGE

66
00:04:41,490 --> 00:04:43,450
THE OPERATION ACCORDINGLY.

67
00:04:43,450 --> 00:04:46,453
WE WERE THE ONES WHO
PROVIDED THIS SITE,

68
00:04:46,453 --> 00:04:49,206
IN THE FACE OF
STRONG PUBLIC CRITICISM.

69
00:04:50,415 --> 00:04:53,219
WE WANT AT LEAST TWO
MACHINES IN RETURN.

70
00:04:56,796 --> 00:04:59,674
(Engine roaring)

71
00:04:59,674 --> 00:05:03,345
Lockon:
ALLELUJAH... KEEP YOUR
SPEED AND ALTITUDE STEADY.

72
00:05:03,345 --> 00:05:04,971
(Gasps)

73
00:05:04,971 --> 00:05:06,473
WOULD YOU STOP ROCKING US?

74
00:05:06,473 --> 00:05:08,141
LOOK, YOU'RE
ASKING A BIT MUCH!

75
00:05:11,895 --> 00:05:14,564
Captain #15A:
OBSERVATION TEAMS,
WHAT IS THE GUNDAMS' TARGET?

76
00:05:14,564 --> 00:05:16,566
SIR, WE HAVE NO UNITS
ALONG THE ROUTE

77
00:05:16,566 --> 00:05:18,318
WHERE WE HAVE
COMM INTERFERENCE.

78
00:05:20,278 --> 00:05:21,863
Kati:
WHAT?

79
00:05:21,863 --> 00:05:23,615
THE GUNDAMS ARE HEADING

80
00:05:23,615 --> 00:05:25,158
STRAIGHT FOR THE
SITE WHERE

81
00:05:25,158 --> 00:05:27,035
THE ENRICHED
URANIUM IS BURIED.

82
00:05:27,035 --> 00:05:28,203
Sergei:
WHAT THE HELL IS THIS?

83
00:05:28,203 --> 00:05:30,121
HOW COULD WE MISS A
GROUP OF TERRORISTS

84
00:05:30,121 --> 00:05:32,457
HEADED STRAIGHT FOR
THE FACILITY?

85
00:05:32,457 --> 00:05:34,459
COLONEL, WE JUST RECEIVED
ORDERS FROM HEADQUARTERS

86
00:05:34,459 --> 00:05:35,794
TO CAPTURE THE GUNDAMS.

87
00:05:35,794 --> 00:05:37,128
(Groans)

88
00:05:38,547 --> 00:05:42,551
I SEE... SO, THIS WAS
ALL JUST A SETUP.

89
00:05:42,551 --> 00:05:45,262
(Cannons fire)

90
00:05:46,471 --> 00:05:49,182
(Boom)

91
00:05:54,104 --> 00:05:56,648
Sergei:
THE GOVERNMENT KNEW WHAT
THE TERRORISTS WERE UP TO...

92
00:05:56,648 --> 00:06:00,110
AND PURPOSELY LEFT THEM ALONE
TO LURE THE GUNDAMS OUT.

93
00:06:06,700 --> 00:06:09,035
DYNAMES HERE.
TARGETED AND READY TO FIRE!

94
00:06:10,662 --> 00:06:11,454
(Boom)

95
00:06:12,122 --> 00:06:12,914
(Bang)

96
00:06:17,460 --> 00:06:18,461
(Boom)

97
00:06:18,461 --> 00:06:19,170
(Crash)

98
00:06:20,422 --> 00:06:22,007
(Boom)

99
00:06:22,424 --> 00:06:24,009
ALL SHOTS ON TARGET!
ALL SHOTS ON TARGET!

100
00:06:24,009 --> 00:06:25,427
LET'S GET GOING,
ALLELUJAH!

101
00:06:25,427 --> 00:06:26,845
ROGER!

102
00:06:26,845 --> 00:06:27,846
(Beeping)
HMM?

103
00:06:27,846 --> 00:06:29,806
(Missiles flying)

104
00:06:29,806 --> 00:06:31,182
IT'S AN ENEMY ATTACK!

105
00:06:35,478 --> 00:06:36,730
(Yelling)

106
00:06:36,730 --> 00:06:38,565
ENEMIES APPROACHING!
ENEMIES APPROACHING!

107
00:06:38,565 --> 00:06:39,899
DAMN IT...

108
00:06:43,361 --> 00:06:44,571
LOCKON!

109
00:06:44,571 --> 00:06:45,238
I KNOW!

110
00:06:51,578 --> 00:06:52,662
(Boom)

111
00:06:58,627 --> 00:06:59,669
(Yelling)

112
00:07:04,466 --> 00:07:06,134
ALLELUJAH!
ENEMIES APPROACHING!
ENEMIES APPROACHING!

113
00:07:11,097 --> 00:07:12,057
WHAT THE...

114
00:07:13,433 --> 00:07:15,101
WHO ARE THESE GUYS?

115
00:07:23,401 --> 00:07:24,402
LOCKON!

116
00:07:30,909 --> 00:07:31,701
LOCKON!

117
00:07:32,619 --> 00:07:34,496
I'M OKAY.
WE'VE GOT INCOMING!

118
00:07:43,254 --> 00:07:44,964
Soldier #15A:
MAINTAIN THE BARRAGE.

119
00:07:44,964 --> 00:07:47,926
KEEP THOSE GUNDAMS
PINNED DOWN!

120
00:07:54,974 --> 00:07:56,142
(Boom)

121
00:08:03,608 --> 00:08:07,153
(Coffee dripping)

122
00:08:16,955 --> 00:08:18,957
WE JUST PASSED
THE SCHEDULED

123
00:08:18,957 --> 00:08:21,501
COMPLETION TIME
FOR THE FIRST PHASE.

124
00:08:21,501 --> 00:08:24,170
I JUST HOPE EVERYBODY MADE IT
OUT OF THERE IN ONE PIECE.

125
00:08:26,131 --> 00:08:28,133
WHAT'S YOUR FORECAST,
MISS SUMERAGI?

126
00:08:29,050 --> 00:08:31,886
I THINK THEY'VE PROBABLY
SWITCHED TO PLAN B2 BY NOW.

127
00:08:35,056 --> 00:08:37,225
IT'S TIME
FOR EXIA AND VIRTUE.

128
00:08:38,309 --> 00:08:40,478
SUCCESSFUL FIRST ATTACK
FOR UNION THREE.

129
00:08:40,478 --> 00:08:43,189
WE HAVE TWO
GUNDAMS AT TF‐4122.

130
00:08:43,189 --> 00:08:45,191
CONTINUE LONG‐RANGE
BOMBARDMENT!

131
00:08:45,191 --> 00:08:47,819
ROGER! CONTINUING
LONG‐RANGE BOMBARDMENT!

132
00:08:47,819 --> 00:08:49,904
GETTING A VISUAL SIGNAL
FROM HUMAN‐ONE!

133
00:08:49,904 --> 00:08:52,323
THEY REQUEST A TEAM BE
DISPATCHED TO POINT TF‐2123!

134
00:08:53,491 --> 00:08:55,869
SO, THEY'RE CHOOSING THE
WEAKEST AREAS TO ATTACK.

135
00:08:56,494 --> 00:08:59,164
DEPLOY THE TWENTY‐THIRD
MOBILE SUIT TEAM IMMEDIATELY!

136
00:09:00,623 --> 00:09:02,792
Operator #15C:
TWENTY‐THIRD MOBILE SUIT
TEAM MOVE OUT!

137
00:09:02,792 --> 00:09:04,544
TWENTY‐THIRD
MOBILE SUIT TEAM MOVE OUT!

138
00:09:07,380 --> 00:09:09,382
COLONEL! HOW AM I
SUPPOSED TO CAPTURE

139
00:09:09,382 --> 00:09:11,301
ONE OF THOSE GUNDAMS
FOR YOU IF YOU WON'T EVEN

140
00:09:11,301 --> 00:09:12,510
GIVE ME THE ORDER
TO LAUNCH?

141
00:09:12,510 --> 00:09:13,511
STANDBY FOR NOW.

142
00:09:13,511 --> 00:09:14,804
COLONEL!

143
00:09:14,804 --> 00:09:18,224
JUST TRUST ME. I'LL MAKE
A MAN OUT OF YOU YET.

144
00:09:19,225 --> 00:09:20,518
UH...

145
00:09:23,938 --> 00:09:27,150
PREPARE TO SWITCH OVER
TO MISSION PLAN B2.

146
00:09:27,150 --> 00:09:31,404
ROGER THAT. EXIA, DISSOLVE
EXTERNAL CAMOUFLAGE MEMBRANE.

147
00:09:31,404 --> 00:09:33,406
I AM NOW COMMENCING MISSION.

148
00:09:38,995 --> 00:09:41,414
Pilot #15A:
I SEE TWO GUNDAMS!
NOTIFY HEADQUARTERS!

149
00:09:48,213 --> 00:09:49,005
(Slash)

150
00:09:52,300 --> 00:09:53,092
(Slash)

151
00:09:53,092 --> 00:10:00,308
♪

152
00:10:00,308 --> 00:10:02,936
THIS IS VIRTUE. IN POSITION
TO SECURE ESCAPE ROUTE.

153
00:10:05,396 --> 00:10:07,148
GN BAZOOKA... BURST MODE.

154
00:10:13,363 --> 00:10:16,825
PARTICLE COMPRESSION
RATE AT 97 PERCENT.

155
00:10:16,825 --> 00:10:19,202
GN PARTICLES...NOW RELEASING.

156
00:10:21,704 --> 00:10:23,289
(Boom)

157
00:10:32,257 --> 00:10:33,132
(Whoosh)

158
00:10:35,176 --> 00:10:36,219
IT'S TIERIA!

159
00:10:36,219 --> 00:10:38,137
THE OTHERS HAVE SWITCHED
TO PLAN B2.

160
00:10:38,137 --> 00:10:40,223
WE'VE GOT TO
GET OUT OF HERE, ALLELUJAH!

161
00:10:40,223 --> 00:10:41,057
ROGER!

162
00:10:43,643 --> 00:10:46,187
FIRST SHOT COMPLETE.

163
00:10:46,187 --> 00:10:48,815
NOW COMMENCING GN
PARTICLE RECHARGE.

164
00:10:55,196 --> 00:10:56,489
THERE'RE SO MANY OF THEM!

165
00:10:56,489 --> 00:10:58,074
A RESPONSE ALREADY?

166
00:11:08,293 --> 00:11:10,920
Lichtendahl:
TWO HOURS SINCE
IT ALL BEGAN.

167
00:11:10,920 --> 00:11:14,465
Christina:
IF THEY'RE ON PLAN B2...
DYNAMES AND KYRIOS SHOULD REACH

168
00:11:14,465 --> 00:11:15,967
THE RENDEZVOUS POINT
PRETTY SOON.

169
00:11:17,844 --> 00:11:20,805
IF WE COULD AT LEAST USE
THE GN ARMS, THEN MAYBE...

170
00:11:21,598 --> 00:11:23,892
BY THIS TIME THEY
SHOULD HAVE SWITCHED OVER

171
00:11:23,892 --> 00:11:26,144
FROM PLAN B2 TO E5.

172
00:11:26,144 --> 00:11:29,355
WHICH MEANS THAT MACHINE
IS GOING TO BE SHOWING UP.

173
00:11:29,355 --> 00:11:30,481
ALLELUJAH...

174
00:11:34,402 --> 00:11:35,486
(Screams)

175
00:11:35,486 --> 00:11:38,656
(Screaming)

176
00:11:38,656 --> 00:11:39,741
ALLELUJAH, WHAT'S WRONG?

177
00:11:39,741 --> 00:11:42,493
MY HEAD IS KILLING ME...

178
00:11:42,493 --> 00:11:43,494
(Screams)

179
00:11:43,494 --> 00:11:45,955
SHE'S COMING...
THE SUPER‐SOLDIER.

180
00:11:45,955 --> 00:11:47,415
(Moaning)
THE SUPER‐SOLDIER?

181
00:11:47,415 --> 00:11:48,541
(Moaning)

182
00:11:48,541 --> 00:11:50,335
YOU MEAN THE HRL MACHINE
FROM YOUR REPORT?

183
00:11:50,335 --> 00:11:52,170
ENEMIES APPROACHING!
ENEMIES APPROACHING!

184
00:11:56,549 --> 00:11:59,677
(Engines roaring)

185
00:12:16,723 --> 00:12:17,724
IT'S HER!

186
00:12:23,354 --> 00:12:24,188
(Gasps)

187
00:12:30,194 --> 00:12:30,987
ALLELUJAH!

188
00:12:33,448 --> 00:12:35,033
WE FELL INTO THEIR TRAP!

189
00:12:39,245 --> 00:12:41,205
(Screaming)

190
00:12:45,585 --> 00:12:48,046
(Missiles ricocheting)

191
00:12:49,964 --> 00:12:52,926
TIERIA! HOW LONG TILL
YOU'RE RECHARGED?

192
00:12:52,926 --> 00:12:54,677
ANOTHER 170.

193
00:12:54,677 --> 00:12:56,554
THAT'S TOO LONG.

194
00:12:56,554 --> 00:12:57,764
(Slam)

195
00:12:57,764 --> 00:12:58,806
(Boom)

196
00:12:58,806 --> 00:13:02,143
(Allelujah screaming)

197
00:13:02,143 --> 00:13:04,395
(Screaming)

198
00:13:04,395 --> 00:13:06,022
I SWEAR THIS...

199
00:13:06,022 --> 00:13:08,942
I WILL COMPLETE THE
MISSION THIS TIME

200
00:13:08,942 --> 00:13:10,401
AS A SUPER SOLDIER!

201
00:13:10,401 --> 00:13:11,945
Hallelujah:
WHAT'S YOUR NAME?

202
00:13:11,945 --> 00:13:13,321
A TRANSMISSION?

203
00:13:13,321 --> 00:13:14,864
COME ON, TELL ME.

204
00:13:14,864 --> 00:13:18,618
SUPER SOLDIER NUMBER ONE,
LIEUTENANT SOMA PERIES!

205
00:13:18,618 --> 00:13:21,162
SOMA PERIES, HEY?

206
00:13:21,162 --> 00:13:23,164
I LIKE THAT.

207
00:13:23,164 --> 00:13:24,958
BUT I'LL LIKE KILLING YOU MORE!

208
00:13:27,460 --> 00:13:28,002
(Gasps)

209
00:13:32,006 --> 00:13:33,633
PULL BACK FOR NOW,
LIEUTENANT!

210
00:13:33,633 --> 00:13:34,550
YES, COLONEL!

211
00:13:38,763 --> 00:13:40,890
(Shots firing rapidly)

212
00:13:41,975 --> 00:13:42,850
NAH...

213
00:13:42,850 --> 00:13:45,311
THIS IS NO FUN.

214
00:13:45,311 --> 00:13:47,563
I'LL LET YOU DEAL WITH
THE REST, ALLELUJAH.

215
00:13:48,439 --> 00:13:49,357
HALLELUJAH!

216
00:13:50,441 --> 00:13:51,567
(Screaming)

217
00:13:57,824 --> 00:14:01,160
Alejandro:
FIVE HOURS HAVE PASSED
SINCE THE FIGHTING BEGAN.

218
00:14:04,706 --> 00:14:06,749
WHERE ARE YOU GOING?

219
00:14:06,749 --> 00:14:10,628
I'M GOING TO HEAR THE OPINIONS
OF THE OTHER OBSERVERS.

220
00:14:10,628 --> 00:14:14,173
IT'S QUITE POSSIBLE MY
JOB COULD BE OVER HERE.

221
00:14:18,594 --> 00:14:21,222
NO, THAT'S NOT WHAT
YOU'RE GOING TO DO.

222
00:14:24,100 --> 00:14:26,102
I HATE ADULTS.

223
00:14:27,061 --> 00:14:29,063
(Shots swarming)

224
00:14:31,232 --> 00:14:32,483
Operator #15B:
SEVENTH MOBILE
SUIT TEAM

225
00:14:32,483 --> 00:14:34,527
HAS REACHED ITS
OPERATING TIME LIMIT.

226
00:14:34,527 --> 00:14:36,279
Kati:
HAVE THE SIXTEENTH MOBILE
SUIT TEAM TAKE OVER.

227
00:14:37,780 --> 00:14:39,824
YOUR TURN'S COMING UP,
LIEUTENANT.

228
00:14:39,824 --> 00:14:42,035
HURRY UP AND GET
READY TO LAUNCH.

229
00:14:42,035 --> 00:14:43,161
MA'AM!

230
00:14:49,459 --> 00:14:52,837
(Missiles whistling past)

231
00:14:52,837 --> 00:14:54,422
(Explosions)

232
00:14:57,925 --> 00:14:59,927
HOW MUCH LONGER
CAN THIS LAST?

233
00:14:59,927 --> 00:15:01,679
THIS ATTACK
IS MURDER!

234
00:15:01,679 --> 00:15:04,474
(Guns firing rapidly)

235
00:15:09,979 --> 00:15:12,023
AT LEAST GIVE US
A BREAK TO EAT!

236
00:15:12,023 --> 00:15:13,232
(Gasping)

237
00:15:19,363 --> 00:15:20,406
(Growls)

238
00:15:20,406 --> 00:15:22,742
THEY WILL NEVER
GET THESE GUNDAMS!

239
00:15:22,742 --> 00:15:27,371
(Panting hard)

240
00:15:31,417 --> 00:15:33,586
Sailor #15A:
OVER FLAGS SQUADRON,
